                <p>Please click on the link below to view the Acceptance.</p>
                <br/>
                <p><a href="_inspection_url" style="background-color: #9E588B; margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px;
                text-decoration: none; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px;">View</a>
