                <p>Hi,</p><br/>
                <p>Reminder to close the activity assigned to you for Acceptance (<b>${object.subject}</b>).</p><br/>
                <p>Click the below link to view Acceptance.</p>
                <p>
                <br/>
                <a href="_inspection_url" style="background-color: #9E588B; margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px;
                text-decoration: none; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 16px;">View</a>
                </p><br/>
                <p>Thank you.</p>
                ]]>
        </field>
    </record>

</odoo>
